# Build context for packages/backend/Dockerfile (context = monorepo root).
# Keep the context lean: the backend image only needs the root package.json and
# the shared-types + backend packages. Everything else is excluded.

# Dependencies — reinstalled fresh inside the image
**/node_modules
.npm

# Build outputs — recompiled inside the image
**/dist
**/build
**/.next
**/out
*.tsbuildinfo
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# The Expo / React Native frontend is irrelevant to the backend image
packages/frontend

# VCS / CI
.git
.github

# Local env & secrets — never bake into the image
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# Expo
**/.expo
**/.expo-shared

# Self-hosted local image store (dev-only backend fallback)
**/.local-image-store

# Logs & temp
**/logs
**/*.log
**/tmp
**/temp
**/coverage
**/.nyc_output

# OS / editor cruft
**/.DS_Store
**/.vscode
**/.idea
*.swp
*.swo

# Docker artifacts
**/Dockerfile
**/.dockerignore

# Misc docs not needed at build time
**/*.md
